examples.bad:
public class MyHandler implements RequestHandler<Request, Response> {
  public Response handleRequest(Request input, Context context) {
    DatabaseClient client = new DatabaseClient(); // BAD: created on every invocation
    return client.query(input);
  }
}

examples.good:
public class MyHandler implements RequestHandler<Request, Response> {
  private final DatabaseClient client = new DatabaseClient(); // GOOD: created once
  public Response handleRequest(Request input, Context context) {
    return client.query(input);
  }
}
